comment: Made this beer during the local Octoberfest. Keged it tonight 18 days later. Initial taste tells me it is young still and needs to mello out a little bit. The wife says it smells a little bit like soy sauce, she thought the same about the wort. But, as a dark beer lover, this came out really well. It was brewed for a party a couple weeks ahead, I think it should reach it's prime about then. Cheers!
